## 🔄 **Vollständiger Agent Workflow**

### **1. Contract Phase**
```bash
# Contract definieren
echo "CONTRACT: [Aufgabe]" > contract.md
echo "ACCEPTANCE CRITERIA:" >> contract.md
echo "- [ ] Kriterium 1" >> contract.md
echo "- [ ] Kriterium 2" >> contract.md

# Bestätigung einholen
cat contract.md
# Warten auf Bestätigung
```

### **2. Setup Phase**
```bash
# WSL aktivieren
wsl
cd /mnt/c/Users/Robin/Projects/StreamMind

# Idempotente Einrichtung
make setup-repo

# Verifikation
make version-current
make help
```

### **3. Development Phase**
```bash
# Branch erstellen
git checkout -b agent/contracts/[name]-$(date +%Y%m%d)

# Development Loop
while [ $? -ne 0 ]; do
    make ci                    # MUSS GRÜN sein
    # Code-Änderungen
    make ci                    # MUSS GRÜN sein
    make commit MESSAGE="msg"  # NUR bei GRÜN
    make wf-monitor MESSAGE="msg"  # MUSS erfolgreich sein
done
```

### **4. Validation Phase**
```bash
# PR erstellen
make pr TITLE="Contract: [name]" BODY_FILE="contract.md"

# Pipeline überwachen
make pipeline-monitor BRANCH=branch-name

# Contract prüfen
cat contract.md
```

### **5. Completion Phase**
```bash
# Erfolg melden
echo "✅ CONTRACT COMPLETED SUCCESSFULLY"
echo "✅ Pipeline is GREEN"
echo "✅ Ready for merge"
```

